'''艾倫·霍奇森·布朗'''（{{lang-en|Ellen Hodgson Brown}}，{{bd|1945年|9月15日||}}）是[[美國|美國]]作家、律師，倡導[[另類醫學|另類醫學]]和金融改革。為「金融公共化研究所」（Public Banking Institute）的創始人和總裁。

== 生平 ==
2011年1月，布朗成立了[[智庫|智庫]]「金融公共化研究所」（Public Banking Institute），該組織主張美國每個州和主要城市都需要一家公共銀行<ref>{{Cite web|title=Public Banks: Key To Freeing America From Wall Street?|url=https://www.mintpressnews.com/public-banks-wall-street/170140/|accessdate=2021-02-04|date=2013-10-08|work=MintPress News|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111223046/https://www.mintpressnews.com/public-banks-wall-street/170140/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=AN ECONOMY OF OUR OWN: AVOIDING ANOTHER JACK-ASS MONETARY CRISIS|url=https://www.vermontwoman.com/articles/2011/1111/monetary.html|accessdate=2021-02-04|date=2011-11-11|publisher=Vermont Woman|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208201346/https://www.vermontwoman.com/articles/2011/1111/monetary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

布朗撰有《債務之網》（''Web of Debt''）、《公共銀行之道》（''The Public Bank Solution''）等書籍<ref>{{Cite web|title=Public banking pitched as alternative financing|url=https://www.sonomanews.com/article/news/public-banking-pitched-as-alternative-financing/|accessdate=2021-02-04|date=2021-01-04|work=Sonoma Index-Tribune|language=en-US}}</ref>。

2013年10月，她在《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》上發表了有關公共銀行的社論文章：〈公共銀行是[[資本主義|資本主義]]的關鍵〉（Public Banks are Key to Capitalism）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Public Banks Are Essential to Capitalism|url=https://www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2013/10/01/should-states-operate-public-banks/public-banks-are-essential-to-capitalism|accessdate=2021-02-04|date=2013-10-01|last=Brown|first=Ellen|publisher=New York Times|language=en|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730134409/http://www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2013/10/01/should-states-operate-public-banks/public-banks-are-essential-to-capitalism|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，布朗代表[[美國綠黨|綠黨]]競選[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]財政部部長。她主張在加州建立一家公共銀行，以解決加州持續的財政危機和[[基礎設施|基礎設施]]資金短缺的問題<ref>{{Cite web|title=Public Banking Advocate, Ellen Brown, Is Running For California State Treasurer|url=https://sandiegofreepress.org/2014/05/public-banking-advocate-ellen-brown-is-running-for-california-state-treasurer/|accessdate=2021-02-04|date=2014-05-08|work=San Diego Free Press|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126160008/https://sandiegofreepress.org/2014/05/public-banking-advocate-ellen-brown-is-running-for-california-state-treasurer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://napavalley.patch.com/groups/elections/p/green-party-announces-statewide-endorsements-for-june-primary-elections|title=Green Party Announces Statewide Endorsements for June Primary Elections|date=2013-12-27|work=Napa Valley Patch|accessdate=2021-02-04|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202101816/http://napavalley.patch.com/groups/elections/p/green-party-announces-statewide-endorsements-for-june-primary-elections|archivedate=2014-02-02}}</ref>。她在2014年6月3日的初選中的得票率為6.5％，沒有資格參加2014年11月4日的正式選舉<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://graphics.latimes.com/calif-primary-election-results-2014/|title=California 2014 primary election complete results|date=2014-06-03|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2021-02-04|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604195937/http://graphics.latimes.com/calif-primary-election-results-2014/|archivedate=2014-06-04}}</ref>。

